# ABOUT THIS SITE

## What is this?

A curated guide to cafes and events in Vadodara.

Life is more than just work and bed rotting.
This site helps you discover experiences actually worth your time.

## The problem

- Too many options, most mediocre
- Instagram is chaotic and unsearchable
- No one you trust is doing the curation
- You waste weekends scrolling instead of going out

## The solution

Ruthless curation. Simple lists. Honest opinions.

Only cafes and events I'd actually recommend to a friend.

## How it works

- I visit places personally
- Rate them honestly (no sponsorships, ever)
- List only the best
- Update weekly with new events

## Design approach

Clean, fast, no BS.
- Near-black backgrounds
- Minimal typography
- Text-first (images when they matter)
- Works on any device

## Who made this

Solo project by Yash.

I'm a designer who codes. This is both:
1. A genuine service for Vadodara locals
2. A portfolio piece showing my design and curation skills

## Tech stuff

- Built with HTML/CSS/JS
- Static site (fast, simple)
- AI-assisted development (Claude, Copilot)
- Hosted on GitHub Pages

## Current status

Early MVP. Testing the concept.

Right now:
- Top 10 cafes in Vadodara
- Weekend events updated regularly
- Text-focused, minimal design

## Philosophy

Quality over quantity.
Honest over hyped.
Experiences over endless scrolling.

